{"tid":497284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"校外派港獨單張 學生組織成員涉藏BB彈槍被捕","createTime":"2017-12-12T14:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T01:00:21.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8a5e1611a57a106a5466e38a0f645f6ff5458b1e","tid":497284,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171212/large/1513089656_4527.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171212%2Flarge%2F1513089656_4527.jpg&h=95ea4e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生組織「學生動源」早前聯同多個本土派和主張港獨的學生組織，在校外派發倡議港獨的傳單。學生動源晚上在facebook指，一名16歲、現就讀中五的男成員，晚上約8時半在立法會示威區，因涉嫌藏有「BB彈槍」被捕，目前已有義務律師及學生動源、其他組織成員前往中區警署了解及協助。<br />\n<br />\n學生動源表示，有關男成員被捕時，同場並沒有其他學生動源成員在場。《蘋果》已向警察公共關係科查詢，正等待回覆。"},{"pid":"9f3447d3c0c88082bcbc03b6188fb063545d3e48","tid":497284,"uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:52:07.000Z","msg":"會唔會開記招話藏有大殺傷力武器"},{"pid":"300bac795f4af7fbffa1aaa94e428eb1e8d36294","tid":497284,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"以前打wargame都會袋住槍返公司...香港持有BB彈槍都犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc43aa273f1173946c67b80c0c47f1f04691f959","tid":497284,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"bb彈槍都犯法？"},{"pid":"5be959208b8b02d46d3034598956f29526d03b66","tid":497284,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"可能換把比佢"},{"pid":"70193ffe6c9d01d718129028e26fc90500ce59b7","tid":497284,"uid":19072,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36c28c35c2aad100326dbf804380b742c8b8bf40","tid":497284,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquo